  <brief_title>The Effects of Hypolipemic and Antidiabetic Treatment on Cytokines</brief_title>
  <acronym>MSF</acronym>
  <official_title>Effects of High and Low Doses of Metformin, Fenofibrate and Simvastatin, Administered Together and in Sequence With Lifestyle Intervention on Lipid Profile, Glucose Metabolism, Low-grade Inflammation and Hemostasis in Patient's Blood Plasma in Type 2 Diabetic Patients With Serious Mixed Dyslipidemia</official_title>
